"```sql\nSELECT \n  (COUNT(*) FILTER (WHERE c.Currency = 'EUR')::float / COUNT(*)::float) * 100 AS percentage_of_KAM_in_euros\nFROM \n  customers c\nWHERE \n  c.Segment = 'KAM';\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the percentage of KAM customers who pay in euros. It filters the customers table to include only those in the KAM segment and then calculates the percentage of these customers whose currency is EUR."